From a unit w/ a S/N of '''LBF104300264''' <small>('''L''' seems to be the '''[[Billionton]]''' vendor code, BTW)</small>... *"122A121-0010 V1.1" is silkscreened on the back of the board. *A sticker with "820300138" printed on it is affixed to the back of the board. *The board is using a single 25.000 MHz crystal (marked "TXC EpOH", "25.000).
